### **AIDA Framework** (Attention, Interest, Desire, Action)
```
Attention: Compelling headline that stops the scroll
Interest: Hook them with a relatable problem or benefit
Desire: Paint the picture of their improved life/business
Action: Clear, specific call-to-action
```

### **PAS Framework** (Problem, Agitation, Solution)
```
Problem: Identify their main pain point
Agitation: Make them feel the cost of inaction
Solution: Present your offering as the perfect fix
```

### **Before & After Bridge**
```
Before: Current frustrating situation
After: Desired outcome/transformation
Bridge: Your product/service as the solution
```

### **Features â†’ Benefits â†’ Outcomes**
```
